<reference id="api_videosurface_enablefilptextureapply">
    <title><ph keyref="enableFilpTextureApply"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc"
        >在渲染时，开启/关闭 Texture 的镜像。</ph></shortdesc>
    <prolog>
        <metadata>
            <keywords>
                <indexterm keyref="enableFilpTextureApply"/>
            </keywords>
        </metadata>
    </prolog>
    <refbody>
        <section id="prototype">
            <p outputclass="codeblock">
            <codeblock props="android" outputclass="language-java"/>
            <codeblock props="ios mac" outputclass="language-objectivec"/>
            <codeblock props="cpp" outputclass="language-cpp"/>
            <codeblock props="electron" outputclass="language-typescript"/>
            <codeblock props="unity" outputclass="language-csharp">public void EnableFilpTextureApply(bool flipX, bool flipY)
        {
            if (FlipX != flipX)
            {
                transform.localScale =
                    new Vector3(-transform.localScale.x, transform.localScale.y, transform.localScale.z);
                FlipX = flipX;
            }

            if (FlipY != flipY)
            {
                transform.localScale =
                    new Vector3(transform.localScale.x, -transform.localScale.y, transform.localScale.z);
                FlipY = flipY;
            }
        }</codeblock>
            <codeblock props="rn" outputclass="language-typescript"/>
           <codeblock props="flutter" outputclass="language-dart"/> 
            <codeblock props="unreal" outputclass="language-cpp"></codeblock></p>
        </section>
        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <note type="attention">
            <ul>
            <li>确保在主线程中调用此方法。</li>
            <li>确保在绑定 VideoSurface.cs 前调用此方法。</li>
            </ul> </note> </section>
        <section id="parameters">
            <title>参数</title>
            <parml>
            <plentry>
                <pt>flipX</pt>
                <pd>是否开启 Texture 在水平方向的镜像：



                    
                    <ul>
                    <li><codeph><ph keyref="true"/></codeph>：开启</li>
                    <li><codeph><ph keyref="false"/></codeph>：（默认）不开启</li>
                    </ul> </pd>
            </plentry>
            <plentry>
                <pt>flipY</pt>
                <pd>是否开启 Texture 在垂直方向的镜像：



                    
                    <ul>
                    <li><codeph><ph keyref="true"/></codeph>：开启</li>
                    <li><codeph><ph keyref="false"/></codeph>：（默认）不开启</li>
                    </ul> </pd>
            </plentry>
            </parml> </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>
